node.text: This is Wings of Rescue. Our sponsor, @titosvodka, will match up to $20,000 in donations sent their way through the link in our bio. Wings of Rescue flies dogs like Clyde from overcrowded shelters and disaster areas to shelters with empty kennel space where they’ll be adopted in no time. They’ve saved 8,597 pets this year already and can save way more with your help. Everyone involved gets a 14/10 from us [EDIT: initial goal of $20k hit in 45 minutes, secondary goal of $40k hit in 3 1/2 hours]

node.accessibility_caption: little golden retriever pup standing on his back legs. he’s on a beach and a wave is crashing behind him. his from arm are outstretched menacingly. his appears to be smiling but do not let that fool you

node.text: Oh c’mon. We only rate dogs. This is a Silly Seaside T-Rex. Please evacuate the beach immediately. Thank you… 13/10 (follow @waylon.the.golden.retriever)

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by WeRateDogs® on September 14, 2021 tagging @ski_the_wonder_dog. May be an image of 1 person, nature and waterfall.

node.text: This is Siri. She heard you’re not supposed to go chasing waterfalls. Went anyway and it was lovely. Not sure why they say that. 13/10 (follow @ski_the_wonder_dog)

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by WeRateDogs® on September 14, 2021 tagging @trupanion, and @retired_and_drooling. May be an image of 1 person and indoor.

node.text: This is Rye. He’s a seaworthy St. Bernarrrd who’s been captain of a pirate crew for ages… or at least that’s what he told his poker buddies. Turns out he may have worked the truth into a bit of a lather. 13/10 (watch our story to learn what really happened, follow @retired_and_drooling)  @trupanion #partner

First Episode tomorrow on our IG Stories ♠️♥️♣️♦️

node.accessibility_caption: A white and grey husky puppy is sitting on a boat with a captain’s hat on. The hat is white, and has a blue bill with yellow trim.

node.text: This is Brixton. He’s the captain now. A little embarrassed because he already misunderstood the purpose of the poop deck. 12/10 happens to the best of us (follow @BrixtonAdventures)

node.accessibility_caption: A white and grey husky puppy is sitting on a boat with a captain’s hat on. The hat is white, and has a blue bill with yellow trim.
A white and grey husky puppy is sitting on a boat with a captain’s hat on. The hat is white, and has a blue bill with yellow trim. It’s now covering his face.
Photo by WeRateDogs® on September 10, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and dog.

node.text:
This is Mo. He has very long legs, which he uses for exceptional zoomies. Last week he zoomed into the dining room table and broke his leg. We’ve covered the remaining cost of the surgery to fix it. Mo is willing to abide by a household speed limit moving forward. 13/10

Accidents like this happen. Please consider getting @Trupanion, so you never have to send us a GoFundMe. It’s best to be puppared ❤️

Click the link in our bio (third one down from there) to get a quote! #partner

node.text: This is Winston. He was born with both an underdeveloped sternum and front arms. His ribs aren’t connected to anything right now so his chest is not properly protected. He needs a series of significant reconstruction surgeries, and he’s growing so fast he needs a new set of wheels every other week. He is a super happy pup who doesn’t know anything’s wrong and you can help him and his rescuers by clicking the link in our bio. 14/10 (he also just made a piglet friend named Wilma) [EDIT: fully funded in 71 minutes]
